The difficulty is in knowing which entites are regulated and which are not . For instance , ENA is an "unregulated" affiliate of a regulated utility ( PGE) . But many utilities have energy services companies affiliates which , while not regulated utilities like San Diego Gas & Electric , are nevertheless heavily regulated . We have tried to figure out what we can in the time available and have relied on readily available public inofrmation .
